Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,惠裡 究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,光輝 抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這麼一回事 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊 早就想得到光輝了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是為了得到他做了點必需的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你喜歡他 表白不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不行 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,表白可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,光輝這麼善良 不會區別待人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就算身邊全是一群毫無利用價值的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,善良的他也不忍心拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,為了讓他成為專屬於我的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須努力把垃圾打掃乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,能來異世界真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要是在日本 打掃垃圾實在太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,當然 我絕對不允許大家回到日本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,光輝要在這個世界和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠永遠生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,惠裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那他們不對勁是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是降靈術啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他們早就已經死掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你騙人 降靈術不可能完成對話交流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛 我的天職可是降靈術師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,往普通的降靈術裡注入生前的記憶和思維
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就能進行一定程度的對話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我的自創版降靈術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且稱之為「縛魂」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只能對剛死亡的個體使用還是挺麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟我可不想讓大家白白喪命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我會讓大家都被有效再利用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 惠裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你這麼做 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不會放過我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,光輝總是這麼善良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我會把你也好好縛魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你變成專屬於我的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,從此你的眼中不再有別人 永遠注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只會對我說我想聽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,專屬於我的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:05:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,光是想像就快讓我欲仙欲死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,惠裡裡 惠裡不可能會做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,禮一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 中村你這王八蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦嗎 不甘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我聽聽你最美妙的悲鳴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,掙扎吧 痛苦吧 詛咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,然而你終究是我的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可笑的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,為眾生之死獻上祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,為可悲之靈予以嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,縛魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 人偶一具製作完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,惠裡 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,鈴 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不論是在日本還是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,為了能待在光輝身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你利用起來真是太方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都覺得光輝身邊只能有雫和香織
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在日本我可是手無縛雞之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,想謀害她們或者讓她們自盡都很費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 有你在真是幫了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,活生生一個大白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我做什麼都會傻呵呵地衝著我笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:07:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谷口鈴的摯友身份實在太好用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,惠裡 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,生氣啦 你這表情真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你最不順眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我會為你安排一個特別的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,任務？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,想想 被久違重逢的摯友殺害的香織
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,會露出怎樣的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,少開玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,難受嗎 痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你看我這麼善良 這就讓你解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 快住手 惠裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再見 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和你假裝做朋友 真是讓我噁心作嘔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 香織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,縛煌鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,雫 堅持住 我馬上去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,香織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,出清淨領域 萬象之母賜福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,求索之人 仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,找尋黑雲邊際之光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你們幾個 怎麼老是來妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,獻上祈禱 接受賜福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 究竟發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,理智點 惠裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這究竟是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,白崎 莉莉安娜公主 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,檜山 你才是 怎麼受這麼重的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,香織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,終於得到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,比起南雲那種人 還是我更好對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯吧 香織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,聖母於此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,…微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,聖天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不會認輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對饒不了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,天翔閃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,玉井 園部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,玉井 千萬別砍到我的手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我才沒這麼菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,鈴 快展開結界 保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,也不能怪她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持住 坂上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我們擋不住 玉井他們會被擊潰的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,滾開 滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,香織
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,天翔閃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,惠裡 檜山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,到此為止了 光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,光輝 為什麼要揮劍向我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我可沒教過你這些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,梅爾德團長 我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,梅爾德團長 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我 光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:13:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,終於奏效了 毒性還挺強的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,既然王子用吻喚醒了公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼公主就用吻讓王子陷入沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然後據為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這種故事也是可以有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,惠裡 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,放心 不是致命毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我會親手殺掉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是剛剛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,再稍微等我一下哦 光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 惠裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦嗎 不甘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我聽聽你最美妙的悲鳴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,掙扎吧 痛苦吧 詛咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然而你終究是我的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可笑的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,為眾生之死獻上祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,為可悲之靈予以嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,緹奧 老師 拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,天輪 不及迴轉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,靈魂既失容器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,沒用的 她都已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}徘徊現世 不渡生死之門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}何不於兩界之間開啟生誕之門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你不和我作對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}祓除死念 重結綻放之靈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我就用魔法復活香織 我的建議如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看周圍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不覺得他們和生前沒什麼兩樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,人都死了還能怎麼辦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,至少變得像他們一樣也不錯對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 還可以對香織為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,為此可不能少了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大意失荊州
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你也一樣嗎 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}糟了 快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心情 目的 我都懶得聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼事的話 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你 要是沒有你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,香織就是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因為你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,別怪別人 你的失敗只能怪你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,從不曾想擔起任何責任的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一條純粹的敗犬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要殺了你 我一定要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你先試試還能不能活下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,至少靈魂的歸位已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不過接下來就要花點時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,最好能借助月的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,已經堅持不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴們的性命不重要了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,城牆外十萬大軍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,傳送門外百萬魔物嚴陣以待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕你們再強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也不可能一邊保護著所有人不停戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼時候說過王國和這些人是我同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想打仗隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 要是你敢妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所見 我會毀滅你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這份恥辱 我一定會讓你償還
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我以神之名起誓 我一定會讓你屍骨無存
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,始 那個傻大個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 那個死垃圾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲 香織 香織她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,希婭 香織就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,香織小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,緹奧 給月她們帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老師也麻煩幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 我們去山頂 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小愛老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小愛老師去救香織吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 園部同學 拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.97,0:21:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,八重檻 別洩氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我們 等我們的好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會讓你再見到香織
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你都這樣了 以後誰來替我們解決麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一定會沒事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 新的旅程
Comment: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------------OP-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:12.72,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:18.72,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:24.06,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:30.49,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:35.91,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:39.66,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.50,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:47.42,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:53.38,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:59.10,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:04.52,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:07.77,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:13.11,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Comment: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:04.05,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,------------------ED------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆為虛空一場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破滅的希望　虛偽的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身體的傷口深不見底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不僅是我　你也背負同樣的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得誰人原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕懷中相擁　徒留輪廓難辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘願承傷不曾猶豫的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹣跚　忍痛離開你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幾步對錯　令我身負百孔千瘡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形單影隻漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　誰人不曾擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
